components.name: Pipeline Initialization
components.description: Marks the start of the pipeline execution.

components.name: Parse Input Parameters
components.description: Extracts DAG run configuration and logical date, formats them, and pushes a compilation configuration to XCom.

components.name: Create Dataform Compilation Result
components.description: Calls Google Cloud Dataform API to create a compilation result using the parsed parameters.

components.name: Trigger Dataform Workflow Invocation
components.description: Initiates a Dataform workflow execution with the compilation result, enabling asynchronous execution and full refresh of incremental tables.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after compilation result is created.

components.name: Monitor Workflow Completion
components.description: Polls the Dataform workflow invocation until it reaches a terminal state (SUCCEEDED or FAILED).

upstream_policy.description: Runs after workflow invocation is triggered.

components.name: Pipeline Completion
components.description: Marks successful termination of the pipeline after the sensor confirms workflow completion.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after workflow completion sensor succeeds.
